13
00:01:35,990 --> 00:01:38,070
Is that enough to find its faults?

14
00:01:38,620 --> 00:01:40,200
Artificial, artificial

15
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:43,370
Hey, how can they stay so sane?

16
00:01:43,370 --> 00:01:46,410
This is their artificial world

17
00:01:46,410 --> 00:01:49,210
In this beautiful world

18
00:01:49,210 --> 00:01:52,550
there is something

19
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:56,050
that obscures all light for me

20
00:01:56,840 --> 00:02:00,430
My heart tries to make sense of it

21
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:02,810
