22
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:04,930
Secret kills for you

23
00:02:04,930 --> 00:02:07,640
Secret kills for you

24
00:02:07,390 --> 00:02:12,190
Secret image for you

25
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:16,570
Don't show me a dark future

26
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:22,910
with this gaudy land

27
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:27,540
Show me a way to fade

28
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:36,050
I'm not on the day shift today... right?

29
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:41,760
You're meeting up with Funahara Yuki and Minase Kaori at Akebonobashi Station at 11:00.

30
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:46,140
At 14:30, you start second shift duty at the Public Safety Bureau.

31
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:48,640
Oh, that's right.

32
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:52,230
What's your room preference today?

33
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:54,520
Victor Horta's Hotel Tassel.

34
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:57,530
Okay! I'll use the library as reference!

35
