The recommended amount for today's breakfast is 240 kilocalories.

38
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:23,590
I'll have a 200 kilocalorie Chinese-flavored breakfast.

39
00:03:23,590 --> 00:03:25,600
Certainly!

40
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,310
It was my very first day on the job...

41
00:03:35,020 --> 00:03:36,150
Why me? What'd I do?

42
00:03:50,330 --> 00:03:53,500
