45
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:03,760
I recommend taking a supplement to prevent mental contamination.

46
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:28,700
I guess this'll do.

47
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,660
All right, see you later.

48
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:34,330
Take care!

49
00:04:42,880 --> 00:04:43,760
So...

50
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:46,260
You messed up, huh?

51
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:50,010
Yeah... though I can't give you the details

52
00:04:50,010 --> 00:04:51,770
since I work for the Public Safety Bureau and all.

53
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:54,480
I don't know much about these things,

54
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:57,900
but what you did wasn't in violation of your duties, right?

55
00:04:58,730 --> 00:04:59,730
I guess not.

56
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:02,610
Then you don't have to worry about it, right?

57
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:05,240
Besides, your Psycho-Pass isn't that clouded either.

58
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:08,120
I guess that means you're not that bothered by it after all?

59
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,910
C'mon, don't be mean!

60
00:05:09,910 --> 00:05:12,250
I didn't get a wink of sleep last night.

61
00:05:12,250 --> 00:05:18,500
I'm surprised the Hue Check showed such a clear color for you, considering what you went through.

62
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:21,210
You don't give yourself much psychological care,

63
00:05:21,210 --> 00:05:22,800
and yet you're such a mental beauty.

64
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:26,340
How do you stay so healthy?

65
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:29,800
Well... Maybe I'm just thick-skinned, you know?

66
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,930
God really is unfair.

67
00:05:33,930 --> 00:05:35,020
You said it.

68
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:40,770
I-In any case... It's not that I doubt the Sibyl System,

69
00:05:40,770 --> 00:05:44,240
but I wonder if a career at the Public Safety Bureau is really right for me.

70
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:47,990
Jeez, you're lucky to even have the choice!

71
00:05:47,990 --> 00:05:50,490
I know you like to speak without thinking, but that's pushing it even for you!

72
00:05:53,330 --> 00:05:55,120
To start with, you were found to have an aptitude for jobs

73
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:58,540
at the Ministry of Economy and the Ministry of Technology,

74
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:01,840
and yet you rejected them both and picked the Public Safety Bureau, right?

75
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:05,840
The best I could do was C-rank scores across the board.

76
00:06:05,840 --> 00:06:09,180
What's the problem? You're good at blue-collar work.

77
00:06:09,180 --> 00:06:13,260
I'm a systems engineer, so my shoulders are always killing me.

78
00:06:14,220 --> 00:06:19,230
Akane, you were an honor student who scored 700 points on the last exam.

79
00:06:19,730 --> 00:06:22,440
You should be able to take on any job with ease, right?

80
00:06:28,570 --> 00:06:31,570
Sorry. I guess we went a little too far.

81
00:06:31,570 --> 00:06:35,870
But I think that if anyone can pull off that job, it's you.

82
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:38,790
And not just because of the aptitude the System indicated.

83
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:41,380
As a friend, I know you'll do well.

84
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:44,300
"That which needs to be done is carried out by those capable of doing it.

85
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:48,050
Such is the grace bestowed upon mankind by Sibyl."

86
00:06:49,930 --> 00:06:51,260
Just kidding.

87
00:07:51,650 --> 00:07:52,950
Excuse me!

88
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:55,490
Is Analyst Karanomori Shion here?

89
00:07:57,580 --> 00:08:00,500
Yeah, yeah. Who are you?

90
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:08,630
I'm Tsunemori Akane. I've been assigned to the CID as of yesterday.

91
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:13,630
Oh! You're the new Inspector who shot Shinya, aren't you?

92
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:18,430
Wow... You're a lot cuter than I thought.

93
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:21,770
That cute face of yours hides how daring you can be, though!

94
00:08:21,770 --> 00:08:26,230
What happened? Did Shinya grab your butt or something?

95
00:08:26,230 --> 00:08:27,940
No. Um...

96
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:31,650
I was told I should come to you to find out how he's doing.

97
00:08:31,650 --> 00:08:33,360
Oh, that.

98
00:08:34,530 --> 00:08:36,990
While I do have a physician's license,

99
00:08:36,990 --> 00:08:40,750
can you believe that's all it took for the government to delegate employee health care to the Analysis Lab?

100
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:44,120
Sure, I may be a latent criminal too,

101
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:48,340
but that doesn't mean they can just slave drive me as much as they want, right?

102
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:50,300
R-Right...

103
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:53,670
Let's see. Akane, was it?

104
00:08:55,470 --> 00:08:58,930
If you're an Inspector, that puts you on the fast track at the Bureau, right?

105
00:08:58,930 --> 00:09:03,140
Hurry up and become a high-ranking official so you can reform the system.

106
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:07,650
You can start by splashing out for a swimming pool and bar lounge at the CID.

107
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:08,810
I'm counting on you!

108
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:13,360
Right, well.. How's Kougami's treatment going?

109
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,450
Oh, that's right.

110
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:24,290
Well, you scored a direct hit on his spinal cord,

111
00:09:24,290 --> 00:09:27,170
