112
00:09:27,170 --> 00:09:32,250
It'll be a little longer before he's able to stand, talk, or anything like that.

113
00:09:37,590 --> 00:09:39,390
Of course, you wouldn't be able to join him in bed right now, either.

114
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:42,180
If you just want to peek in on him, that'd be okay.

115
00:09:42,180 --> 00:09:43,020
What do you wanna do?

116
00:09:43,770 --> 00:09:46,350
W-Well, I'd better not bother him.

117
00:09:46,810 --> 00:09:50,980
If he spends today resting, the aftereffects should go away.

118
00:09:50,980 --> 00:09:53,610
Come back tomorrow morning.

